sentences.english: This is all but the revival of Alexandrian thought.
sentences.chinese: 這是所有的，但復興亞歷山大思想。

sentences.english: An ancient city of northern Egypt east of Alexandria. It was the site of a great temple honoring Serapis.
sentences.chinese: 坎努帕斯埃及北部一座古老城市，位於亞歷山大東部。

sentences.english: Now Alexander is going to reveal a secret of how to cook a sandwich from McDonald’s.
sentences.chinese: 現在亞歷山大要揭密如何製作麥當勞三明治了。

sentences.english: Days after Alexander's death, she had Stateira poisoned.
sentences.chinese: 亞歷山大死後沒多久，她毒死了斯塔蒂娜。

sentences.english: In this room you can also find Aleksandr’s easel and palettes.
sentences.chinese: 在這個房間你也可以發現亞歷山大的畫架和調色板。

sentences.english: So, Alexander is putting himself forward as divine.
sentences.chinese: 所以亞歷山大標榜自己爲神。

sentences.english: Alexander McQueen in 2010 released a set of armadillo shoes.
sentences.chinese: 亞歷山大麥克奎恩在2010年發佈了一套犰狳鞋。

sentences.english: Dr Alwan graduated in Medicine from the University of Alexandria.
sentences.chinese: 他畢業於亞歷山大大學，專業爲醫學。

sentences.english: Mr. Alexander launched a scathing attack on Labour's campaign tactics.
sentences.chinese: 亞歷山大先生對工黨的競選策略發起猛烈進攻。

sentences.english: It is a lesson that human architecture will have to learn, or re-learn — with far-reaching implications.
sentences.chinese: 亞歷山大一直專注於將這些經驗轉換利用到建築上。

sentences.english: Memorial services were held aboard the Directorate flagship Aleksander.
sentences.chinese: 追悼儀式在地球聯邦旗艦亞歷山大號上舉行。

sentences.english: Alexander thinks Artest is the missing piece to a championship-caliber team.
sentences.chinese: 亞歷山大認爲，阿泰斯特就是總冠軍那塊拼版。

sentences.english: Alexander II is very clear, if not abandoned the small profits, then the Italian there is no guarantee.
sentences.chinese: 亞歷山大二世很清楚，若不棄小利，則大利難保。

sentences.english: After the Persians it was Alexander the Great's turn.
sentences.chinese: 繼波斯帝國之後，阿富汗的統治者是亞歷山大大帝。

sentences.english: Welcome to Four Seasons Hotel Alexandria at San Stefano, Egypt.
sentences.chinese: 歡迎來到埃及聖斯特凡諾亞歷山大四季酒店。

sentences.english: During the evening there were performances from Alexander Acha and Ana Barbara.
sentences.chinese: 在晚上有從亞歷山大阿查和安娜芭芭拉表演。
